    "description": "Introducing the sequel to our captivating<strong> solitaire game</strong>, now set in an exotic environment with exciting new gameplay mechanics. Here, you'll find everything you need for a <strong>perfect vacation</strong> – vibrant locations, varying difficulty levels of solitaire, <strong>hidden object levels</strong>, and a heartwarming love story.<br><br>Vacation is the perfect time for changes in your personal life. Dive into the unpredictable tale of a <strong>love triangle</strong> and find out who wins the heroine's heart! Experience incredible adventures in love and on the game levels!<br><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br>- 200 stunning and vibrant solitaire levels<br>- Hidden object levels with various mechanics<br>- Hidden gnome on solitaire locations<br>- Decorating your own flower shop<br>- A bright and unpredictable love story<br><br>Love, adventure, the ocean, and captivating solitaire levels are waiting for you! 🌺🌴💖<br><br>Jump into this tropical paradise, and let the magic of love and adventure sweep you off your feet!",
